sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI
    participant TestRunner
    participant PytestBackend
    participant Pytest

    User->>CLI: python runner.py --test tests/test_two_sum.py
    CLI->>CLI: parse_args()
    CLI->>TestRunner: run(test_path)
    TestRunner->>PytestBackend: execute(test_path)
    PytestBackend->>Pytest: subprocess.run("pytest test_path")
    Pytest-->>PytestBackend: exit_code, stdout, stderr
    PytestBackend-->>TestRunner: ExecutionResult
    TestRunner-->>CLI: ExecutionResult
    CLI-->>User: print summary
